snippet.title: Up and Adam!
snippet.description:
Welcome to Up and Adam Live!  
This is our channel to converse with our favorite celebs, discuss reality TV and chat about pop culture!

❤️ → THANK YOU SO MUCH FOR SUPPORTING OUR CHANNEL!
Your donations allow us to keep trucking along, grow and increase our quality!
A million thanks to everyone.  From the bottom of my heart, I love you all!
